{
  "chapter": 99,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在郭府订婚宴前叮嘱乌果通知滕翼防备信陵君手下入宫偷取《鲁公秘录》。郭秀儿含泪将凤形玉坠赠予项少龙，表达无法结合的深情。宴会上赵致为纪嫣然和赵雅传话打趣，气氛轻松。突然赵兵冲入禀报王宫起火，赵雅行宫被焚毁，三十人遇难包括侍婢小昭。孝成王暴怒问责，项少龙立下军令状承诺日出前缉拿凶徒。滕翼查明凶徒藏于韩闯行馆，项少龙推理出三晋合一大计与韩闯包庇信陵君的关联，当面揭破韩闯，迫其合作。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三爷这么快便走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_guo",
      "text": "立即通知二爷，信陵君遣派了一批不知人数多少的高手前来邯郸，极可能趁今晚入宫偷取《鲁公秘录》，教他设法防备。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "禁卫军和我们城卫泾渭分明，除非有孝成王之命，否则我们踏入宫门半步也会给赶出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_guo",
      "text": "请二爷设法使人监视王宫，若有疑人，便跟踪他们看在何处落脚。唔！都是只动用我们自己的人较好一点，多留心例如地道那一类出口，说不定信陵君有办法得到王宫秘道的资料，又或藏有内应也难说得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生！请等一等。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要和董先生说两句话，你们退到一旁去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "父命难违，秀儿别无选择，先生可明白秀儿的心意吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秀儿不能把身体献与先生，便由这玉坠代替，假若先生对秀儿尚有点情意，请把它挂在身上吧！秀儿死而无憾了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "高帛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "雅夫人早嘱咐小人，要与董将军同席，将军请随小人来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "高帛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "将军请入座。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然姊叫我问你溜到哪里去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "方便也不行吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "方便哪用这么久的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "致致何时变成传声筒，告诉她凡事可大可小，老天爷都管不着。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天是夫人问的，她说郭秀儿和你先后脚进来，又神色有异，是否刚给你窃玉偷香，拔了李园的头筹？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "致致恨不得立把田单碎尸万段，不过人家却不急，因为知道董爷定会为致致作主。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "多想点快乐的事不是更好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "致致全听董爷吩咐！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "赵兵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董将军不好哩！王宫起火了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "全是蠢材，若贼子的对象不是物而是寡人，寡人岂非……哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡何在！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "找到那批凶徒了，他们藏在韩闯的行馆里。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "绝错不了，小俊率人亲自跟踪他们，看着他们进入韩闯的行馆，现在他们正密切监视着那里，保证他们即使会飞也走不了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这城守是怎么当的，连贼人入城都不知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "凶手早潜伏城内，只是等到今晚动手而已！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你怎敢说得如此肯定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "此事如无内应，实教人难以相信，无论时间、情报、来去无踪的方式，均是天衣无缝，绝非仓促可成。所以末将敢断言，凶徒定是在邯郸潜伏一段长时间，到今晚才觑准时机动手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "大王何不让董将军去主持搜索敌人的行动，好让他戴罪立功？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "寡人限你三天之内，把贼子找出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_cheng_xu",
      "text": "给我把这蠢材关到牢子里，若找不到贼人，就拿他作陪葬。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还不给寡人去办事？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "如此小事一件，何用三天时间，明天日出前，宫内失去的东西将会放在大王案上，凶徒则会一个不漏地给大王缉捕回来，就算死了也让大王见到尸首。若办不到，我董马痴不用大王动手，也无颜再见明天的太阳。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董将军要到何处拿人？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "自然是到韩侯落脚的行馆去，韩侯难道以为贼子会躲在别处吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "将军说笑了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "真人面前哪容说假话，念在韩侯恩德，而董某亦知韩侯不知贼子会辣手至此。现在事情仍有挽回的余地，只看韩侯肯否合作，否则有什么后果，韩侯不会不清楚吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 291
    }
  ],
